dct_description_sm: U.S. Coast Survey ; triangulation by S.C. McCorkle, 1869 ; topography by A.M. Harrison, 1869 ; hydrography by F.P. Webber, 1868 ; verified, J.E. Hilgard.
Also covers adjacent portion of Narragansett Bay.
Depths shown by soundings and contours.
Includes information on tides and soundings.
